room_title: Escape room "Escape Annabelle" by Deadlock Escape in St. Louis
room_description:
Our escape room is an experience like unlike anything you have seen before. For enthusiasts, by enthusiasts, this truly is “a new breed of escape room”. With one of a kind puzzles, more rooms than ANY other escape room in the Saint Louis area, and a creepy thrilling theme based off of the real story of Annabelle.

The scene is set in an old home, your job is to find Annabelle. She’s free, she’s angry, and she’s out to get you. Come find her in record time and make it into our high-score board.
